# People

Relationship context. Who matters, what's open with them, what's coming up.

> **How to populate:** Start with the 15–20 people you interact with most. For each, capture: relationship, where they live, last contact, open thread, anything coming up. Update during weekly review. Apply the 3-week rule — if someone hasn't surfaced in 3 weeks, archive them (you can always re-add later).

